        "type": "text",
        "content": "技术要求：\n定子引出线按GB/T 7345-2008要求：\n对定子三相线，每根引出线应能承受34.5N的拉力，\n试验后，引出线不能断开，绝缘层和线芯不能损坏。",
        "content_en": "Technical requirements:\nStator leads: GB/T 7345-2008.\nEach phase lead withstands 34.5N tensile force,\nAfter test: no broken lead; no insulation/core damage.",
